<div class="flex flex-col min-h-full bg-red-50 text-gray-700 leading-6 font-sans h-screen h-60">
  <%= render "navbar" %>
  <main class="pr-4 pl-4 max-w-5xl w-full ml-auto mr-auto">
  <p class="text-center italic max-w-2xl mr-auto ml-auto text-gray-600">
  This single-page quote editor was build with Turbo and... a single line of custom JavaScript for the flash message animation. If you want to learn how it is made, you can read the Turbo Rails tutorial.
  </p>
 <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 justify-between mt-3">
    <h1>Quotes</h1>
      <%= link_to "New quote",
                new_quote_path,
                class: "btn btn-active btn-secondary" %>
  </div>
   <%# <div class="flex justify-center px-4 py-16 bg-base-200">Hello!</div>
    <button id="request">Make SWAPI request</button>
    <div id="response"></div> %>
  </main>
</div>

<script>
  document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
  const responseDiv = document.getElementById("response");
  const button = document.getElementById("request");

  button.addEventListener("click", () => {
    fetch("https://swapi.dev/api/planets/1/")
      .then((response) => response.text())
      .then((text) => (responseDiv.innerHTML = text));
  });
});

</script>